My husband and I really liked it. I added extra vinegar, lots of salt and some dried parsley for color. I would definitely prepare it again!

Rating: 2
I liked this recipe but I think that the other spicy gazpacho is better. This one had a slightly bitter aftertaste. Could have been the tomatoes or something else. I made this for a dinner party. I will not make it again. There are other recipes that i prefer.

Rating: 3
I made a double batch of this gazpacho for a Fourth of July picnic and everyone loved it. Some of the picnic-goers were spice-shy, so I used only one jalapeno. It was still good, but I will use two jalapenos next time. The soup travels well.

